790
01:26:22,632 --> 01:26:23,433
Plai.

791
01:26:24,034 --> 01:26:25,057
Uteč.

792
01:26:25,139 --> 01:26:26,573
Plai, rychle uteč

793
01:26:26,622 --> 01:26:27,745
běž uteč.

794
01:26:56,842 --> 01:26:58,177
Je pozdě

795
01:27:07,512 --> 01:27:09,544
